{"build_type":"library","description":"Discipline allowlist data: the only functions permitted to read the raw process boundary directly (array_read base __argv, or call read_all_of_stdin). Every other function must obtain its request through the runtime seed parse_argument_vector_json_request. Members: dispatch_capability_gated_json_request (the shell = outer POSIX adapter), load_link_run_native_objects (the loader/runner entry), compile_job_from_stdin_into_native_elf + resolve_package_closure_main + return_first_stdin_input_byte (compiler-internal stdin readers). Data only; parsed once at first use by ensure_discipline_allowlists_parsed.","module_name":"error-rawio-reading-allowlist-json-document","package_name":"error-rawio-reading-allowlist-json-document","function_definitions":{"error-rawio-reading-allowlist-json-document":{"return_type":"str","parameter_definitions":[],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"allowlist","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"{\"dispatch_capability_gated_json_request\":1,\"dispatch-capability-gated-json-request\":1,\"load_link_run_native_objects\":1,\"compile_job_from_stdin_into_native_elf\":1,\"resolve_package_closure_main\":1,\"return_first_stdin_input_byte\":1}"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"allowlist"}}]}}}